  HTTPAPI -->|contains| APIRPOST
  HTTPAPI -->|contains| APIRHEALTH
  HTTPAPI -->|uses stage posture| APISTAGE
  HTTPAPI -->|invokes through| ROLEAPIGW
  APIRPOST -->|invokes| IGLAMBDA
  APIRHEALTH -->|invokes| IGLAMBDA
  IGLAMBDA -->|executes with| ROLELAMBDA
  IGLAMBDA -->|uses ingress contract| IGLAMBDAENV
  IGLAMBDA -->|deduplicates in| DDB
  IGLAMBDA -->|sends failures to| DLQ
  IGLAMBDA -->|publishes admitted traffic to| TTRAFFIC
  IGLAMBDA -->|reads handles from| SSM
  IGLAMBDA -->|writes logs to| CWLAMBDA

  DDB -->|managed by access role| ROLEDDB
  TTRAFFIC -->|is transported by| MSK
  TTRAFFIC -->|schema-governed by| GLUEREG

  CWLAMBDA -->|feeds| CW
  CWWSP -->|feeds| CW
  SFN -->|feeds metrics to| CW
  EVID -->|feeds operational evidence to| DASHOPS
  CW -->|feeds live posture to| DASHOPS
  EVID -->|feeds spend/proof evidence to| DASHCOST
  BUDGET -->|feeds budget posture to| DASHCOST

